1. *Sveti* ovaj dan kako bi mogao da podeliš svoje veselje sa drugima (Sanctify this day in order to be able to share your joy with others).

2. Ona je *sveto* očuvala svoju devojačku čast (She kept her maiden honour sacred).

3. On je *svetio* mnogo vremena svojoj porodici (He devoted a lot of time to his family).

4. Učenik je *svetio* veče učenju (The student devoted the evening to studying).

5. Vojnik je *svetio* svoj život svojoj zemlji (The soldier devoted his life to his country).